========
README
========

Changes to PS1 so it will show git status,
and some eyecandy.

It requires to download some scripts from the git's git repo.
Links in the file.


Just save the file in ~ as ".mini0n-bash" 
and add this to the end of your .bashrc
to load the changes:


# ==== PS1 with git and eyecandy ====
source .mini0n-bash.sh

